snippet.title: Succubus Forest - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
A village is invaded by succubi each night. On a quest to defeat them, you enter the Succubus Forest, which is home not only to succubi, but many monster girls that will attack you without mercy. You must fend them off and reach the heart of the forest.

Succubus Forest on Kagura Games Store: https://www.kaguragames.com/product/succubus-forest/
